category: MEDICAL SPECIALTIES
category comment: 

clue: An M.D. in this medical branch deals in the treatment of mental, emotional & behavioral disorders

response: psychiatry

clue: Nuclear medicine is a subspecialty of this field that involves the use of X-rays to diagnose & treat disease

response: radiology

clue: Palliative medicine goes hand in hand with this type of end-of-life care, providing comfort to both the patient & their family

response: hospice

clue: From Greek & Latin for "new birth", this type of doctor specializes in the care of newborns & premature babies

response: a neonatologist

clue: This type of surgeon operates specifically on the organs in the chest including the heart, the esophagus & the lungs

response: cardiothoracic (thoracic)

